Tom Ford Bailey Sunglasses:
Tom Ford a world-famous lifestyle brand offers this pair of bailey sunglasses that offer a fine blend of style and comfort to the wearer. With metallic branding on the temple and brown full-rim frame these sunglasses can be an apt choice for a classy look. While going out with friends on a road trip you can wear these fashionable sunglasses from Tom Ford with a shirt and pair of jeans.
